name: Inter
bio: Sport Club Internacional, commonly known as Internacional, Inter de Porto Alegre or simply Inter, is a Brazilian professional football club based in Porto Alegre.

player.name: Taison
player.bio: Taison Barcellos Freda, simply known as Taison, is a Brazilian footballer who plays as an attacking midfielder for Campeonato Brasileiro Série A club Internacional

name: Grêmio
bio: Grêmio Foot-Ball Porto Alegrense, commonly known as Grêmio, is a Brazilian professional football club based in Porto Alegre, capital city of the Brazilian state of Rio Grande do Sul.

player.name: Pedro Geromel
player.bio: Pedro Tonon Geromel is a Brazilian professional footballer who plays for Grêmio as a centre-back.

name: Santos
bio: Santos Futebol Clube, commonly known simply as Santos or Santos FC, is a Brazilian sports club based in Vila Belmiro, a bairro in the city of Santos. It plays in the Paulistão, the State of São Paulo's premier state league, as well as the Brasileirão, the top tier of the Brazilian football league system.

player.name: Marinho
player.bio: Mário Sérgio Santos Costa, commonly known as Marinho, is a Brazilian footballer who plays for Santos as a forward.

name: Flamengo
bio: Clube de Regatas do Flamengo, more commonly referred to as simply Flamengo, is a Brazilian sports club based in Rio de Janeiro, in the neighbourhood of Gávea, best known for their professional football team

player.name: Gabriel Barbosa
player.bio: Gabriel Barbosa Almeida, commonly known as Gabigol or Gabi, is a Brazilian professional footballer who plays as a forward for Campeonato Brasileiro Série A club Flamengo and the Brazil national team.

name: Corinthians
bio: Sport Club Corinthians Paulista is a Brazilian sports club based in the Tatuapé district of São Paulo.

player.name: Willian
player.bio: Willian Borges da Silva, known as Willian, is a Brazilian professional footballer who plays as a winger or as an attacking midfielder for Corinthians. Willian started his career at Corinthians, before joining Shakhtar Donetsk in August 2007 for a fee of €14 million

name: Bragantino
bio: Red Bull Bragantino, commonly known as Bragantino, is a Brazilian football club based in Bragança Paulista, São Paulo. It competes in the Série A, the top tier of the Brazilian football league system, as well as in the Campeonato Paulista Série A1, the highest level of the São Paulo state football league.

player.name: Bruno Praxedes
player.bio: Bruno Conceição Praxedes, known as Bruno Praxedes or just Praxedes, is a Brazilian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Red Bull Bragantino.
